SELECT   a/data[at0001]/events[at0002]/data[at0003]/items[at0004]/value as T1_dv_text,
  a/data[at0001]/events[at0002]/data[at0003]/items[at0005]/value as T1_dv_coded_text,
  a/data[at0001]/events[at0002]/data[at0003]/items[at0008]/value as T1_dv_quantity,
  a/data[at0001]/events[at0002]/data[at0003]/items[at0011]/value as T1_dv_count,
  a/data[at0001]/events[at0002]/data[at0003]/items[at0012]/value as T1_dv_date_time,
  a/data[at0001]/events[at0002]/data[at0003]/items[at0015]/value as T1_dv_ordinal,
  a/data[at0001]/events[at0002]/data[at0003]/items[at0019]/value as T1_dv_boolean,
  a/data[at0001]/events[at0002]/data[at0003]/items[at0020]/value as T1_dv_identifier
        FROM EHR e CONTAINS COMPOSITION c
            CONTAINS (OBSERVATION a[openEHR-EHR-OBSERVATION.supported_data_types.v0])
 LIMIT 1
        ORDER BY c /context/start_time/ value DESC
